NOTE ON VENDORED MOD SOURCE (advanced/):

The advanced/ directory contains text/source files from third-party Space
Engineers mods, vendored for study and reference. Those files remain the
property of their respective authors (ARYX/AWE, Mod Adjuster, Definition
Extension API, BuildInfo by Digi, Animation Engine by Math0424, Mother OS by
Agentluke) under their own licenses. The MIT license above applies to this
repository's own documentation and tooling, not to that vendored third-party code.
